{"tid":1797712,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"全香港sales同我入黎","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T09:09:26.000Z","uid":210495,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a4c24c0d3d1d22c5f5f755bb8f1c0337cede79","tid":1797712,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"如果你賣波鞋做多過7年<br />\n如果你做專櫃做多過7年<br />\n總之所有sales 如果你做多過7年<br />\n就合資格登記做批發及零售界選民！<br />\n<br />\n有巴打整理左所有功能界別嘅入場資格，發現sales係可以幫手做批發及零售界嘅個人選民。<br />\n[新職業解鎖] 推銷師 - 7500人用30分鐘多3票，就可以奪取功能組別&amp;選委會，推三萬黑警入獄及釋放義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782837</a><br />\n<br />\n個人會員申請link(&gt;=7年零售/服務/相關工作經驗)：<a href=\"https://www.hkrma.org/b5/retail_membership/joinus_iam.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrma.org%2Fb5%2Fretail_membership%2Fjoinus_iam.php&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=d27ed8d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkrma.org/b5/retail_membership/joinus_iam.php</a><br />\n<br />\n填完上面份form，交埋年費，再填埋REO43<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=3ddaa057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n搞掂！Share出去！"},{"pid":"dc5cf4ea370217cc70c69e99697dde69289c9225","tid":1797712,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:03:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"12a39da523f5a26899e81912a53b8c72d3a669c3","tid":1797712,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65c534e733385d56b130052