8408866601f7b8deae7959ec","tid":1797712,"uid":38929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"請留意，你要符合下列條件，先可以符合資格登記做選民<br />\n --&gt;「 (a) 你是「有權」 在以下團體的大會上「表決」 的該團體的成員或會員」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/wr_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fwr_c.pdf&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9c4ae9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/wr_c.pdf</a> ( 原文睇 p.11 附錄乙 )<br />\n<br />\n而登記做「香港零售管理協會」嘅「個人聯席會員」<br />\n--&gt; 係團體的周年大會是「沒有投票權」的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkrma.org/b5/retail_membership/joinus_iam.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrma.org%2Fb5%2Fretail_membership%2Fjoinus_iam.php&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=d27ed8d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkrma.org/b5/retail_membership/joinus_iam.php</a>  ( 原文睇「會員權利」第3條 )<br />\n<br />\n結論，登記做「香港零售管理協會」嘅「個人聯席會員」係唔符合資格登記做功能組別選民。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yORd5L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyORd5L2.jpg&h=caa37005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ca8zQcJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCa8zQcJ.jpg&h=3ecea196&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}